\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Overview of our pipeline. For each VLM, we extract decoder activations from bilingual image--caption pairs, train sparse autoencoders (SAEs) to decompose activations into interpretable features, identify gender-associated features via differential activation analysis, and perform targeted ablation during caption generation to test causal claims. Cross-lingual analysis compares English and Arabic feature sets.}}{3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{1}{3}}
